      <description>&lt;p&gt;I am currently a second-year Ph.D. student in the &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.cs.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/cs/index.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Department of Computer Science and Technology&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/thu2018en/index.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Tsinghua University&lt;/a&gt;, advised by &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.xlhu.cn/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Prof. Xiaolin Hu&lt;/a&gt;. I received the B.E. degree from the Department of Computer Science and Technology, Huazhong University of Science and Technology in 2018.
I was a research intern from August, 2017 to July, 2018 at &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.sensetime.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;SenseTime&lt;/a&gt;, working with &lt;a href=&#34;https://amandajshao.github.io/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Dr. Jing Shao&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;My research interest includes deep learning and computer vision.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
